{"tid":1509683,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"雨傘革命嘅失敗經驗令我地害怕同政府有任何形式嘅會議 但係而家嘅我地根本唔需要驚","createTime":"2019-08-27T02:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T03:15:06.000Z","uid":213747,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6df9cacff8fb2e379b4fe075283b102846f78e90","tid":1509683,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"閉門會議?呸 你咪繼續捉住班牛鬼蛇神圍爐傾計囉垃圾政府<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>只有以承諾回應五大訴求為前設嘅會議先係抗爭者認可嘅會議</strong></span></span><br />\n因為今次反送中運動冇大台,冇人真係可以完全代表民間同政府談判<br />\n往後就算邊個自稱代表民間行入去談判我都唔會割席,<br />\n而會否被清算之類嘅風險請自行斟酌<br />\n唯獨五大訴求係所以抗爭者嘅最大公因數,其他講咩都係假<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"72868730afe8f08939cb593a49e6ae8bedcbcb15","tid":1509683,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQruu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=917be166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQruu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=f87bb4ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQruu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=0f7b590f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"82fb30495c0780